## Limitations
The data on late-term abortions is subject to limitations due to variations in reporting standards and definitions of what constitutes a late-term abortion. Additionally, political and social factors may influence the availability and reporting of such data. The estimates provided are based on available data, which may not capture all instances of late-term abortions due to underreporting or lack of comprehensive data collection in certain regions.

